class CK_SKIPJACK_PRIVATE_WRAP_PARAMS provides the parameters to the CKM_SKIPJACK_PRIVATE_WRAP mechanism.

PKCS#11 structure:

    CK_ULONG ulPandGLen;

    CK_BYTE_PTR pRandomA;
    CK_BYTE_PTR pPrimeP;

  } CK_SKIPJACK_PRIVATE_WRAP_PARAMS;
